  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Set in the mythical world of ancient Japan, players take on the role of ninja warrior Shinobi. To free the world from the curse of Goaku, Shinobi must recover 5 elemental swords and defeat the Shoguns who wield them. It will take stealth, strength, and the mastery of the mystic arts for Shinobi to battle his way through the 5 lands.\n\nWhile the game shares a name with the third game in the Shinobi series, it's a stand-alone spin-off title not based on the previous game.",
